snippet.title: TV Schedule | Cartoon Network Show Listings
snippet.description: Find a complete schedule of local listings for all your favorite shows. Discover what to watch and when to find it on Cartoon Network.

snippet.title: Super 80's
snippet.description: The kids from Super 8 try to keep the 80's from taking over the town! Watch more MAD on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: 8-Bit Destruction
snippet.description: After Gumball prank texts Ocho, Ocho rains destruction down on Gumball and Darwin. Watch more of The Amazing World of Gumball on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: "Starter Pack" - TV Spot
snippet.description: Mordecai and Rigby try to protect Thomas from Muscle Man's pranks. Watch Regular Show Mondays at 8/7c!

snippet.title: Behind the Scenes - Sunburn
snippet.description: Getting a little sun is good for you, but actor Connor Del Rio definitely overdid it. He shows off his major burn behind the scenes of last night's episode. Slap on some serious SPF and check out Level Up, Tuesdays at 8/7c on Cartoon Network!
